        <trans-unit id="103" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Setting the instance mode of a service enables you to specify when a <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=nameWithType&gt;</ph> (and its associated user-defined service object) is created.</source>
